{"tid":1451373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"！！基督徒/天主教徒/全部人請入，入黎為香港禱告，必能看見神蹟！！","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T13:04:56.000Z","uid":292762,"like":223,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":130,"replies":[{"pid":"15aa9e1bcc476929a8e632b661750a0208a4ee08","tid":1451373,"uid":292762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:54:12.000Z","msg":"入左黎呢個post嘅基督教/天主教徒，或者唔係教徒，都同我一齊每人打一兩句甚至一段禱文（非教徒就咁打句阿門就可以），在這動盪不安的時代，卻需要一班基督徒開始為這世代祈求平安，因為聖經這樣說：你們要為那城求平安，為那城禱告耶和華；因為那城得平安，你們也隨着得平安。耶利米書 29:7 <br />\n<br />\n讓我們一同為香港求平安求公義，將神的祝福帶到香港！<br />\n<br />\n親愛的天父：<br />\n香港正處於動盪不安的世代，政府無能，警察濫權，不公義的事在香港處處發生！我們每天也感到很無力！<br />\n神啊！我知道你是個公義，憐憫，施慈愛的神，只要我們不住祈求，神蹟必彰顯在地上，你的公義必降臨在地上。<br />\n神啊！求你將撒旦擊退，將仇敵遠離香港，使香港恢復原有的樣貌，不義的事挪去，不許撒旦在香港運行。<br />\n願你的靈運行在每一個香港人的心中，願你旨意成就在地上，願你配得所有敬拜和讚美！<br />\n奉主名求，阿門！<br />\n<br />\n係唔係基督徒都好，都希望你係樓下幫手講阿門，幫手推一推讓更多人可以一齊祈禱祝福香港！或者幫手打一兩句禱文！<br />\n<br />\n願神祝福各位香港人！！！"},{"pid":"b2c15b9b754dd70a3d6c6c218444f6589397c0f5","tid":1451373,"uid":292762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:55:53.000Z","msg":"阿門"},{"pid":"d903019711d8a97797efe0eecefda2d8149a5b00","tid":1451373,"uid":292762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:56:35.000Z","msg":"阿門"},{"pid":"0b99800cc11096e915754b10bb67319630f912da","tid":1451373,"uid":292762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:56:45.000Z","msg":"阿門"},{"pid":"6d3952518231086c5746590d93725ef642cd9012","tid":1451373,"uid":292762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:56:58.000Z","msg":"阿門"},{"pid":"f70953f4de5392e98042221ea77e70cbdc635dfe","tid":1451373,"uid":292762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:57:09.000Z","msg":"願神祝福香港！"},{"pid":"24edb7ea90348289526c4d2945e81492bd332946","tid":1451373,"uid":230427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:03:14.000Z","msg":"各自出力！ 無論有無信仰 請留低你既禱文！<br />\n<br />\n&lt;長期戰爭&gt;祈禱求神報應降災區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1450745\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1450745</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3bcd9302a1fc9fd1bbea21f93594951a5517f340","tid":1451373,"uid":230427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:03:24.000Z","msg":"幫推！"},{"pid":"43189473cef619840a9e0d62b92c3bcff5b86a00","tid":1451373,"uid":290531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:03:29.000Z","msg":"God bless HK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5615c112350863698b10d45659193cf5ed62fa","tid":1451373,"uid":230427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:03:43.000Z","msg":"求神憐憫香港人"},{"pid":"c389864c4d069674552056ecb645d2c33434a543","tid":1451373,"uid":292762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:04:40.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"f27e4e89658b4a55be39fb1f6cc66b674ce3ea6f","tid":1451373,"uid":290852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:05:52.000Z","msg":"求主的公義彰顯。"},{"pid":"385f768c2bf407a6ed66cada5aea09150924d27f","tid":1451373,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:05:54.000Z","msg":"由小處到大局，至絕處到出路，香港人的宿命，邁進勝利之道。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1450774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1450774</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3d24b3c106f5e339bc5763925552ba383a20a76c","tid":1451373,"uid":216253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:06:38.000Z","msg":"amen."},{"pid":"00152a61c9d43d5fb0b36c1b16f7e407cafe2765","tid":1451373,"uid":248384,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:06:59.000Z","msg":"其實佢不仁 我地何需講道義<br />\n勇武用武後 請進入民居 引佢傷及無辜<br />\n迫佢地用彈 正所謂事不關已 已不勞心<br />\n中間派唔care係因為冇波及佢地<br />\n當有樓既 樓價下跌 影響到佢地<br />\n佢地會出黎屌示威者<br />\n當721 佢地仔女受傷 佢地會出黎屌黑警<br />\n我地要做既係<br />\n引發更多人抗議反抗<br />\n光環？道德高地？係極權暴政下有咩用<br />\n睇下黑警用咩手段拘捕<br />\n嬲？可以形容到？<br />\n與其日日外國頭條<br />\n不如自己香港自己救"},{"pid":"ab959ab40114a721a65378448befe74a29ee6759","tid":1451373,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:07:25.000Z","msg":"幫手推<br />\n<br />\n記者會共識<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449180</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0e45b7772ccab933566a422e5f3374fc945ed37e","tid":1451373,"uid":260262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:09:38.000Z","msg":"我地一定會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ce51c8f9db12ce742bbb5c70020ff8f1b5a619","tid":1451373,"uid":281692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:10:33.000Z","msg":"主佑香港，惡人必滅亡。阿們！"},{"pid":"e3784b107009608c680063e61bef9c0bb5acb111","tid":1451373,"uid":258402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:10:56.000Z","msg":"求主幫助世人尋回仁義與良知，擦亮雙眼<br />\n願主公義降臨"},{"pid":"4c52ed8e8a4a7e683ee18f2399fdd843283472a8","tid":1451373,"uid":292762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:11:20.000Z","msg":"！！基督徒/天主教徒/全部人請入，入黎為香港禱告，必能看見神蹟！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451373\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451373</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f8063aa5d9df24ac388b59f37bbf84e37e308d13","tid":1451373,"uid":292762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:11:30.000Z","msg":"！！基督徒/天主教徒/全部人請入，入黎為香港禱告，必能看見神蹟！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451373\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451373</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dced795d9bc99c2852eb2b9f679505403e8cd15a","tid":1451373,"uid":44298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:13:02.000Z","msg":"我想信天主教，有冇推介，定係去是但一間教堂就得？"},{"pid":"5e87f5894b1bf4b296da424240920f93f291de9c","tid":1451373,"uid":225875,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:13:08.000Z","msg":"聽日去機場祈禱會"},{"pid":"042d16785a97f7b6adbf37005d078f80ebc47034","tid":1451373,"uid":112042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:13:34.000Z","msg":"阿門"},{"pid":"4f8e783fcf4442a26a1af55ce5e1c4202517f242","tid":1451373,"uid":282449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:14:09.000Z","msg":"天父，祈求祢摧毀邪惡的政權，叫不仁不義的當權者自食惡果！"},{"pid":"7118f13ec29ec61470bb58dad208ad74b37b20e5","tid":1451373,"uid":68861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:14:10.000Z","msg":"阿門"},{"pid":"2d707704414dd4f1f85f63f387e02f1beac53062","tid":1451373,"uid":169869,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:14:24.000Z","msg":"詩篇94:<br />\n<br />\n求使驕傲的人有應得的報應<br />\n<br />\n1 耶和華啊，你是伸冤的神。<br />\n伸冤的神啊，求你發出光來。 <br />\n2 審判世界的主啊，求你挺身而立，<br />\n使驕傲人受應得的報應。 <br />\n3 耶和華啊，惡人誇勝要到幾時呢？<br />\n要到幾時呢？<br />\n<br />\n4 他們絮絮叨叨說傲慢的話，<br />\n一切作孽的人都自己誇張。 <br />\n5 耶和華啊，他們強壓你的百姓，<br />\n苦害你的產業。 <br />\n6 他們殺死寡婦和寄居的，<br />\n又殺害孤兒。 <br />\n7 他們說：「耶和華必不看見，<br />\n雅各的神必不思念。」<br />\n<br />\n8 你們民間的畜類人當思想，<br />\n你們愚頑人到幾時才有智慧呢？ <br />\n9 造耳朵的，難道自己不聽見嗎？<br />\n造眼睛的，難道自己不看見嗎？ <br />\n10 管教列邦的，就是叫人得知識的，<br />\n難道自己不懲治人嗎？ <br />\n11 耶和華知道人的意念是虛妄的。<br />\n為耶和華懲責訓誨者其人有福<br />\n<br />\n12 耶和華啊，<br />\n你所管教、<br />\n用律法所教訓的人是有福的！ <br />\n13 你使他在遭難的日子得享平安，<br />\n惟有惡人陷在所挖的坑中。 <br />\n14 因為耶和華必不丟棄他的百姓，<br />\n也不離棄他的產業。 <br />\n15 審判要轉向公義，<br />\n心裏正直的，必都隨從。<br />\n<br />\n16 誰肯為我起來攻擊作惡的？<br />\n誰肯為我站起抵擋作孽的？ <br />\n17 若不是耶和華幫助我，<br />\n我就住在寂靜之中了。 <br />\n18 我正說「我失了腳」，<br />\n耶和華啊，那時你的慈愛扶助我。<br />\n19 我心裏多憂多疑，<br />\n你安慰我，就使我歡樂。<br />\n<br />\n20 那藉着律例架弄殘害、<br />\n在位上行奸惡的，<br />\n豈能與你相交嗎？ <br />\n21 他們大家聚集攻擊義人，<br />\n將無辜的人定為死罪。 <br />\n22 但耶和華向來作了我的高台，<br />\n我的神作了我投靠的磐石。 <br />\n23 他叫他們的罪孽歸到他們身上。<br />\n他們正在行惡之中，<br />\n他要剪除他們；<br />\n耶和華我們的神要把他們剪除。"},{"pid":"db8591e52ed6479bf972a1f72599a6f4e3362140","tid":1451373,"uid":211565,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:14:46.000Z","msg":"不如我地祈禱會<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0a7e597982dab9c34a2ccc724933543ce96376","tid":1451373,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:15:35.000Z","msg":"文宣<br />\n<br />\n另一戰線: 防止中共藍絲去人化!!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451397\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451397</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"755df69a93813915dee75e30ae1c95a4c8af1c68","tid":1451373,"uid":155019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:16:41.000Z","msg":"阿門"},{"pid":"baa0cde1656cfa8c2b28bcb7dda3bbb8d2fbef40","tid":1451373,"uid":283668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:19:24.000Z","msg":"小編按：有醫護人員透露，指今晚眼部中槍的女生情況非常嚴重，現正準備進行緊急手術。有醫護人員與我們均認為人權組織需嚴正跟進事件，請各位替那位搶救中的女生祈禱。<br />\nFC: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/161014811328873/posts/489157275181290?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F161014811328873%2Fposts%2F489157275181290%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaBSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=c00596ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/161014811328873/posts/489157275181290?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"c9d2b7276a29ac694eb546a804814c34e9217d33","tid":1451373,"uid":288956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:21:35.000Z","msg":"阿門"},{"pid":"be2af8269771b27d26382a849fc96d1c5d33ff4b","tid":1451373,"uid":28307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baa0cde1656cfa8c2b28bcb7dda3bbb8d2fbef40","tid":1451373,"uid":283668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:19:24.000Z","msg":"小編按：有醫護人員透露，指今晚眼部中槍的女生情況非常嚴重，現正準備進行緊急手術。有醫護人員與我們均認為人權組織需嚴正跟進事件，請各位替那位搶救中的女生祈禱。<br />\nFC: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/161014811328873/posts/489157275181290?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F161014811328873%2Fposts%2F489157275181290%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaBSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDS